<p class="ql-align-center">成了天空的主角</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一时间，摩天大楼都变得暗淡了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人们的眼睛里、汽车的后视镜中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">都变成了火烧云的舞台</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200824/a21b860c97424e398dca57f9d5857a5b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200824/b7e9791f097e4ab18062dec4b91d0bce.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">透过树叶的缝隙</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">远处的云彩也愈显壮观</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">树影婆娑、河水荡漾</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">晚霞坠落在河面上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">摇摇晃晃泛起粉色的波光</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200824/3369da51d5a346e0a667ab765f340e4a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200824/2a463bb359534f27886014ba42a92b4d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">倘若走到山顶之上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">漫山遍野的绿与热浪翻腾的红</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">构成一幅撞色的优美画卷</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200824/075a11dfaaf64b73b58442e22fbb91a6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200824/a3f9d671a2694882b5bc40a4ea7fc016.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200824/e52e8742fddd48df88c756bccec560be.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">城市的日落可能会被高耸的建筑物遮挡</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有时这不是遗憾</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而是一种别样的美</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这个城市一定有很多人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">被这场温柔的晚霞治愈</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200824/b176ff6d16264f9c8a3993753b90f95a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
